{
  "stem": "16571.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I finished up in a-- this big building.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I went in there, and there was thousands of suits and jackets and trousers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And I discarded my stripes, and I got into this-- fitted myself out like I was going to a wedding in this lovely suit.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I was so tired, I fell asleep on somebody else's [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And When I got up, I was-- lice were crawling on me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And this time, I went voluntarily out, went up to a soldier, and I said, come on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Do it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Sort of.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And you know, little things which flash back to-- to you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And I mean, something like that, you never forget if you live to 120.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And that's-- that's-- that's things would happen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And you know, gradually people were dying like flies because the German-- the British came in, and they were giving people to conserves.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Corned beef.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Tins of corned beef.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And very fatty foods.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And they were eating one minute and bringing it back-- round the backside the next minute.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "They were dying like flies in the thousands.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "They were not used to the food and all that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "Me, coming from a little village, I was more interested in a-- in a potato rather than in a-- a tin of spam or whatever.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And by the time they realized what was happening, what they were doing, they stopped it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "They opened kitchens.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "They used to issue us with a ticket to line up for dinners.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And they-- we lined up for dinners, and we had like more or less what you get here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "Self-service.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
